body_html: @tfboyd great to know you guys are looking at it! I think their multi-GPU resnet example is especially intriguing. It's basically fork of official cifar multi-GPU example which I think was originally made by @shlens and doesn't have obvious problems like feed_dict, yet there's a large performance gap with competitors.
